[{"Id": 1014236, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Near the tombs of Imam al-Hadi and Imam al-Askari (a), there lies the tomb of Husain the son of Imam al-Hadi (a) and the brother of Imam al-Askari (a) as well as other tombs of great personalities from the descendants of the Holy Prophet (ie. sayyids). Husain son of Imam Naqi (a) seems to have been one of the sublime and great personalities. Some traditions have mentioned that Imam Hasan Askari (a) and his brother Husain were called the two grandsons, being resembled to the two grandsons of the Holy Prophet (s); namely, Imam Hasan (a) and Imam Husain (a) the sons of Imam Ali (a).", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Moallif kehte hai keh yeh baat sab ko maaloom hai keh Imam Ali Naqi (a) wa Imam Hasan Askari (a) ki qabre mubarak ke nazdik bohot se sadaat’e azaam ke marqad hai, un mein ek Janabe Husain bin Imam Ali Naqi (a) hai jo wahan dafn hai. Agar-che mujh ko Janabe Husain ke halaat tafseel ke saath maaloom nahi huwe to bhi yeh zaroori jaanta hu keh aap ek buland martaba aur buzurg-tar sayyad thay, baaz riwaayat se pata chalta hai keh Imam Hasan Askari (a) aur aap ke bhai Janabe Husain ko sibtain kaha jaata tha aur dono buzurg-waaro’n ko apne do buzurgaan Imam Hasan (a) aur Imam Husain (a) ki awaaz apne inhi chacha Janabe Husain ki awaaz jaisi thi.", "UrduDescription": "مولف لکھتے ہیں: یہ بات سب کو معلوم ہے کہ امام علی نقیؑ و امام حسن عسکری ؑ کے مرقد مبارک کے نزدیک بہت سے ساداتِ عظام کی قبور ہیں ان میں ایک جناب حسین ابن امام علی ؑ نقی ہیں جو وہاں دفن ہیں اگرچہ مجھ کو جناب حسین کے حالات تفصیل سے معلوم نہیں ہیں تو بھی یہ ضرور جانتا ہوں کہ آپ ایک با مرتبہ اور بزرگ سید تھے، بعض روایات سے پتہ چلتا ہے کہ امام حسن عسکری ؑ اور آپ کے بھائی جناب حسین کو سبطین کہا جاتا تھا اور دونوں بزرگوں کو اپنے دو بزرگوں امام حسنؑ اور امام حسین ؑ کے ساتھ تشبیہ دی جاتی تھی۔ نیز ابوالطیب سے مروی ہے : حجۃ ابن الحسن ؑکی آواز ان کے چچا جناب حسین کی آوازجیسی تھی۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014237, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "According to the tradition reported by Abul Tayyib, the voice of Imam Mahdi (a) was similar to the voice of Husain. In his book of Shajarat Awliya, Sayyid Ahmad Ardagaani Yazdi, the wise jurisprudent and traditionist, mentioning the sons of Imam Ali al-Hadi, says that his son Husain was one of the famous ascetics and worshippers and he professed the Imamate of his brother.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shajaratil Auliya jo Faqi o Mohaddis Hakeem Sayyad Ahmed Ardagaani Yazdi ki Taaleef hai us mein mazkoor hai keh Imam Ali Naqi (a) ki aulaad mein Janabe Husain thay keh jo bade aabid o zaahid aur apne bhai Imam Hasan Askari (a) ki Imamat ke moteqad thay ta ham agar koi shakhs kuchh aur jus-ta-joo kare to shaayad woh unke mazeed ausaaf o fazaael daryaaft kar paayega jo unki buzurgi ko ziyadah waazeh karenge.", "UrduDescription": "شجرۃ الاولیا (جو فقیہ و محدث حکیم سید احمد اردکانی یزدی کی تالیف ہے) میں مذکور ہے کہ امام علی نقی ؑ کی اولاد میں جناب حسین تھے جو بڑے عابد و زاہد اور اپنے بھائی امام حسن عسکری ؑ کی امامت کے معتقد تھے تاہم اگر کوئی شخص کچھ اور جستجو کرے تو شاید وہ ان کے مزید اوصاف و فضائل دریافت کر پائے جو ان کی بزرگی کو زیادہ واضح کریں گے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "A